com.machinepublishers.jbrowserdriver

Class Timezone

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.machinepublishers.jbrowserdriver.Timezone

  • public class Timezone
extends Object
    Browser timezone and daylight savings settings. Currently one limitation is that locale for formatting of date strings will always be en-US.
